  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "`TARGET_AGGREGATORS_PER_COMMITTEE` was chosen to be 16 for phase 0 without too much thought.\r\n\r\nI'd like to at least consider reducing this to 8 in Altair to reduce the load on the global channel (especially considering that an intended optimization didn't work out --  #2183).\r\n\r\nIssue is a placeholder and a temperature gauge. Haven't done any analysis one way or the other yet.\r\n\r\n",
